iol&amp;publication_year=2001&amp;pages=358&amp;doi=10.1007%2Fs002470100436&amp;pmid=11373927">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">55.</div><div id="R55" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content"><span class="named-content" data-type="arthw-firstauthor"><span class="named-content" data-type="arthw-snm">Emura</span><span class="named-content" data-type="arthw-fnm">A</span></span>, Kudo S, Mihara M, Matsuo Y, Sato S, Ichigi Y. Testicular malignant lymphoma: imaging and diagnosis. <em>Radiat Med</em>1996;14:121–126.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8827805/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Radiat+Med&amp;publication_year=1996&amp;pages=121&amp;pmid=8827805">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></section></div><div class="core-collateral" role="dialog" aria-modal="true"><div id="core-collateral-info" data-active-pane="false"><header><h2><i class="icon-info" aria-hidden="true"></i>Information &amp; Authors</h2></header><section id="tab-information" role="tabpanel"><h3>Information</h3><section class="core-self-citation"><h4>Published In</h4><div class="core-journal-presentation">



        
