<div class="core-journal-description"><div property="isPartOf" typeof="Periodical"><span property="name">RadioGraphics</span></div><div class="core-enumeration"><span property="isPartOf" typeof="PublicationVolume">Volume <span property="volumeNumber">27</span></span> • <span property="isPartOf" typeof="PublicationIssue">Number <span property="issueNumber">5</span></span> • <span property="datePublished">Sep 1 2007</span></div><div class="core-pagination"><span class="heading">Pages</span>: <span class="content"><span property="pageStart">1335</span> - <span property="pageEnd">1354</span></span></div><div class="core-pmid"><span class="heading">PubMed</span>: <a class="content" href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17848695/" property="sameAs" target="_blank" title="Link to PubMed">17848695</a></div></div></div></section><section class="core-copyright"><h4>Copyright</h4><div role="paragraph">© RSNA, 2007.</div></section><section class="core-history"><h4>History</h4><div><b class="core-label">Published online</b>: Sep 1 2007</div></section><section class="core-permissions"><h4>Permissions</h4><div>Request permissions for this article.</div><div><a class="btn" href="https://marketplace.copyright.com/rs-ui-web/mp/search/all/10.1148%2Frg.275065157">Request Permissions</a></div></section><section property="keywords"><h4>Keywords</h4><ol><li><a href="/action/doSearch?AllField=CNS+%3D+central+nervous+system&amp;stemming=yes&amp;publication=radiographics" alt="Search on this keyword" rel="nofollow">CNS = central nervous system</a></li><li><a href="/action/doSearch?AllField=FDG+%3D+fluorodeoxyglucose&amp;stemming=yes&amp;publication=radiographics" alt="Search on this keyword" rel="nofollow">FDG = fluorodeoxyglucose</a></li><li><a href="/action/doSearch?AllField=HD+%3D+Hodgkin+disease&amp;stemming=yes&amp;publication=radiographics" alt="Search on this keyword" rel="nofollow">HD = Hodgkin disease</a></li><li><a href="/action/doSearch?AllField=NHL+%3D+non-Hodgkin+lymphoma&amp;stemming=yes&amp;publication=radiographics" alt="Search on this keyword" rel="nofollow">NHL = non-Hodgkin lymphoma</a></li></ol></section><section class="core-article-notes"><h4>Notes</h4><div role="paragraph">Diagnostic imaging modalities have a fundamental role in the staging of lymphomas, making surgical staging unnecessary in most cases; familiarity with the spectrum of imaging findings is essential for radiologists to enable them to provide guidance for the treating physicians.</div></section></section><section id="tab-contributors" role="tabpanel"><h3>Authors</h3><section class="core-authors"><h4>Affiliations</h4><div id="con1" property="author" typeof="Person"><div class="heading"><span property="givenName">Paolo</span> <span property="familyName">Toma</span>, <span property="honorificSuffix">MD</span></div><div class="content"><div class="affiliations"><div property="affiliation" typeof="Organization"><span property="name">From the Departments of Radiology (P.T., C.G.), Neuroradiology (A.R.), and Oncology (A.G.), Giannina Gaslini Children’s Hospital, Largo Gaslini 5, 16147 Genoa, Italy. Presented as an education exhibit at the 2005 RSNA Annual Meeting. Received August 24, 2006; revision requested November 14 and received February 28, 2007; accepted March 26. All authors have no financial relationships to disclose.</span></div></div><div class="core-author-link"><a href="/authored-by/Toma/Paolo" rel="nofollow">View all articles by this author</a></div></div></div><div id="con2" property="author" typeof="Person"><div class="heading"><span property="givenName">Claudio</span> <span property="familyName">Granata</span>, <span property="honorificSuffix">MD</span></div><div class="content"><div class="affiliations"><div property="affiliation" typeof="Organization"><span property="name">From the Departments of Radiology (P.T., C.G.), Neuroradiology (A.R.), and Oncology (A.G.), Giannina Gaslini Children’s Hospital, Largo Gaslini 5, 16147 Genoa, Italy. Presented as an e